I wait.  It waits.  It disappears once again into the darkness.<br>
My thoughts turn to the bright light in my dark universe,  the unwavering constant in my life, my beautiful and glorious Charizma…<br>
<br>
Pain.  The pain of a child lost.  That torturous wracking pain and sorrow.<br>
